OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FDo not lose heart over     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fconflicts, archbishop says 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The Archbishop of Canterbury has used  
OL,6, his Easter sermons to say "we must not 
OL,7, lose heart" over the war in Ukraine or 
OL,8, the situation in Israel and Palestine. 
OL,10,FPreaching at Canterbury Cathedral on   
OL,11,FEaster Sunday, Justin Welby said that  
OL,12,F"true peace is no aimless daydream".   
OL,14,FThe resurrection teaches Christians    
OL,15,Fthat "life triumphs over death, light  
OL,16,Fover darkness", he added.              
OL,18,FHe also warned that those who "oppress 
OL,19,Fand subjugate others" will "face divine
OL,20,Fjustice".                              
